values: Well I set up my dark room and I have to say Im happier then Ive been in a long time. I have a new Saunders/LPL enlarger and a full place to print color and b&w photos. I Tested it out last night and it works wonderfully. I have to say making the rooms light tight was a pain in the ass though. Five trips to home depot.....ugh. Hope everybody had a happy V-day. I spent mine alone with my chemicals. yeah.

More updates later. Long ones. As for now Im in Miami sorting through and dealing with my grandfathers possesions, will, and etc. Its been tough but I've been learning some family history in theprocess. Ill be back friday.

At 6:11 am EST my grandfather passed away in Miami. From were he was born in Cuba to the US he akllways showed kindness, passion, and intelligence. The world is worse off with losing a wonderful man such as him. I am glad he is in less pain but saddened by the fact that he had to go. 
The funeral is on tuesday morning and I have a long drive ahead of me. I wish my family could get together under happier circumstances. I still have no idea where I'm staying and politics are getting in the way of me bringing a co-driver. 
Thank you to <lj user="in_effigie"> for keeping me company in the hard time today. I needed it.
When it rains, it pours.

I feel stagnated. I feel like I'm wasting away in my house cause I dont have enough money to get gas to drive anywhere. Bills are piling up and I just need a job. :(  

ugh!

Im taking things a day at a time.

I think thats all I can do. 

I miss having friends to hang out with............. Ive been in my apartment too long.......
The records are getting finished though so im not to idle. 
Oh, and I desprately need a job......

I have a new studio space. 3 iso booths and for the first time ever I have glass in between them! I have to tune the rooms though :(.......... Thats allways a pain in the ass. I wonder where I am going to rent a sound shooter. Maybe I'll call mark.

It'll be good when my label releases it's records next month. I really need to get off my ass and working on them. Ive been procrastinating to much. 

I'm s thankful to the couple friends I have for their patience. I know I've been going nuts. Thanks for tolerating it.

The fianlity of it is killing me.
I wish it wasnt permanent.

I don think I've ever been this close......The ultimate act of shame.......
I don't think I ever understood till now.....
Guilt of another prevents my mode.
Silent I brood, cry, gaze.
There is no tomorrow, just an endless expanse of void.
I can not eat. I can not sleep.
A simple release is all I crave but will never receive.
Even if I became the man I need to be the battle is lost forever.

I can barely see.
I can barely breathe.
Im not going to make it.

I lost something irreplacable tonight i think. 
I have no hope left.

I have an interview on Tues. afternoon. I feel like I'm going backwards. Guitar center......uck. Well at least i get gear discounts. I could really use a new set of studio monitors.      
I feel stagnated. Like nothing new is hapening. Like Im stuck in some replaying story made to make people laugh at the charachters bad luck. I have reent for this month but after that i just dont know. I think I have to start looking at other options.
She never called to cancel today.
I havent been out of my room for 48 hrs. I suppose I should but I think in a way Im afraid of what will happen if I do.  I think Ill be staying in tonight also.  Maybe Ill make more top ramne.
yeah :(

I had a horrible birtday.

I didnt do one thing right today. 
I didnt show what I needed to show.
I didnt act how i needed to act.
It nothing new I suppose.....shooting myself in the foot. More aptly in the heart........
Ive commited emotional suicide more times than i can count.....
I hold on in all the wrong ways......
I cant let go though, I just dont know how to control my heart  when it screams out to do something.
I should learn the harder I try to grip, the more it slips away......
I wish I could just be the person I need and want to be.
I simply not good enough.
I know it sounds dramatic but thats what I was told by three people today.
I think they are right. 
When will I have the strength to be the person I need to be.
With time can trust ever be truely earned back.
I need to scream but I know i dont have the courage.
My thought are now in fragments not phrases.

I am devoid of speech so these describe how i feel.

O, never say that I was false of heart,
Though absence seem'd my flame to qualify.
As easy might I from myself depart
As from my soul, which in thy breast doth lie:
That is my home of love: if I have ranged,
Like him that travels I return again,
Just to the time, not with the time exchanged,
So that myself bring water for my stain.
Never believe, though in my nature reign'd
All frailties that besiege all kinds of blood,
That it could so preposterously be stain'd,
To leave for nothing all thy sum of good;
For nothing this wide universe I call,
Save thou, my rose; in it thou art my all.
Shakespear's sonnet 109

In faith, I do not love thee with mine eyes,
For they in thee a thousand errors note;
But 'tis my heart that loves what they despise,
Who in despite of view is pleased to dote;
Nor are mine ears with thy tongue's tune delighted,
Nor tender feeling, to base touches prone,
Nor taste, nor smell, desire to be invited
To any sensual feast with thee alone:
But my five wits nor my five senses can
Dissuade one foolish heart from serving thee,
Who leaves unsway'd the likeness of a man,
Thy proud hearts slave and vassal wretch to be:
Only my plague thus far I count my gain,
That she that makes me sin awards me pain.
sonnet 141

Your type is: INTP

INTP - "Architect". Greatest precision in thought and language. Can readily discern contradictions and inconsistencies. The world exists primarily to be understood. 3.3% of total population. 

INTPs are very logical, analytical people who like to think about concepts and ideas, searching for the perfect solution to problems. They are detached, intellectual, and complex, always looking for different challenges. INTPs are very independent, skeptical and often brilliant. They are able to stay calm, even in the most difficult situations. INTPs are intolerant of redundancy and slow people, and are bored by simple issues. They are likely to ignore any rules, people or tasks they consider trivial. One thing they often consider trivial is emotion, their's and other's. Because of this they don't realize that other people need praise and reassurance, and INTPs are usually not good with relationships. They are intensely private, and very hard to get to know. INTPs are highly selective about with whom they will share their ideas, and they won't share their deepest feelings with anyone. They dislike and distrust authority, only respecting knowledge. 

INTPs are on a constant search to understand everything, and learn everything they can. They learn anything they decide is worth the effort at an incredible speed, and are able to apply the knowledge to other areas immediately. INTPs have a natural skill for finding flaws in projects and logic, and at findingsolutions to the problems. They are good at thinking up ideas, and starting projects, but they often lose interest or ignore the details of it, and it doesn't end as well as they had hoped. INTPs work best alone, and when in groups they seem detached and rarely contribute. They have creative imaginations and see possibilities where others don't. INTPs have a global perspective, and are more interested in theories than their practical applications. 

They are not very good at sharing their complex thoughts and ideas, and in conversation they will often pause to think. INTPs are not very appearance-conscious and often look slightly disheveled. They also are not generally well-understood, and feel slightly isolated.
